    <h2 class="big">Titel</h2><p>"Alles beim Teufel - Die Comedia" <i>nach Ben Jonsons "The devil is an ass"</i></p>
    <h2 class="big">von</h2><p>Holger Ptacek, Samar Ertsey</p>
